Apache SIS™ Coordinate Reference System (CRS) codes

This list is generated from the EPSG database version 8.9, together with other sources. All those Coordinate Reference Systems (CRS) are supported by the Apache SIS™ library version 0.7, except those with a red text in the last column. There is 5811 codes, 96% of them being supported.

Notation:

  • The ↷ symbol in front of authority codes (33% of them) identifies left-handed coordinate systems (for example with latitude axis before longitude).
  • The codes with a strike (8% of them) identify deprecated CRS. In some cases, the remarks column indicates the replacement.
